# Copy to `.env` for local data fetches. NEVER commit the real key.
# In CI it comes from the GitHub Actions secret APISPORTS_KEY instead.
#
# Get a free key at https://dashboard.api-football.com (100 requests/day).
APISPORTS_KEY=your_api_football_key_here

# Optional overrides (the fetcher defaults to these):
# APISPORTS_LEAGUE=1
# APISPORTS_SEASON=2026
